params.buyoutPrice: The price (in Wei) for which the fractionalized NFT can be be bought for from the contract.

params.erc20Supply: The total supply of the newly created ERC20 token.
params.erc20Symbol: The symbol of the newly created ERC20 token.
params.nftContractAddress: The address of the NFT that is to be fractionalized.
params.nftTokenId: The token ID of the NFT that is to be fractionalized.

returns._0: The ID of the newly created fractionalized NFT.
